@startuml 06-seq-catalog-search
title Sequence — Catalog Search (with Redis Cache)

actor Customer
participant "React SPA" as SPA
participant "Catalog Service" as Catalog
database Redis
database PostgreSQL

Customer -> SPA: Enter search query
SPA -> Catalog: GET /catalog/books?q=...

Catalog -> Redis: GET cache key

alt Cache hit
  Redis --> Catalog: Cached result
  Catalog --> SPA: 200 { books }
else Cache miss
  Redis --> Catalog: nil
  Catalog -> PostgreSQL: SELECT books WHERE ... (indexed)
  PostgreSQL --> Catalog: Result rows
  Catalog -> Redis: SET cache key (TTL 5 min)
  Catalog --> SPA: 200 { books }
end

SPA --> Customer: Display results
@enduml
